{"tid":517857,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"令女！有圖！美婦做手術被拍裸照提告 醫生稱只是「開玩笑」","createTime":"2018-01-02T17:06:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-02T18:09:49.000Z","uid":42407,"like":2,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7e86b034c6539518ee0a4d2ff71f81f93ca73cba","tid":517857,"uid":42407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T17:06:09.000Z","msg":"美國一名女子在一所醫院接受手術時，竟被主診醫生和護士拍下裸照。<br />\n<br />\n45歲的哈魯斯基（Sheila Harosky）是賓夕凡尼亞州華盛頓醫院的手術室秘書，去年她接受手術，並康復後正常上班，但其中一位同事給她看手機裏當時為她進行手術時所拍下的裸照。<br />\n<br />\n哈魯斯基就事件向院方投訴，但醫院指照片只是開玩笑，在她手術前把一條假腸放在身上拍的，並非有意。雖然哈魯斯基承認這是醫生開的一個玩笑，但她說沒有允許拍照。因此，院方把涉事護士解僱，又禁止該醫生再做手術，哈魯斯基其後申請假期，當她放假回到醫院繼續工作時反而被解僱。她指，醫院當她是犯錯者而非受害人，於是決定提出控訴。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89833ef3b6f54ccd2324ba78774759face10f851","tid":517857,"uid":42407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T17:06:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c52fcf481c083f4821fddad9a8720bf7c5a4a847","tid":517857,"uid":42407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T17:07:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9d963cd9e0a0266776d4960fa56a3ece384e44d","tid":517857,"uid":44083,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T17:07:43.000Z","msg":"令你老母臭閪"},{"pid":"ee93a54dd076efbc7297c5f7f407d483ad1a3a61","tid":517857,"uid":42407,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"a9d963cd9e0a0266776d4960fa56a3ece384e44d","tid":517857,"uid":44083,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T17:07:43.000Z","msg":"令你老母臭閪"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T17:09:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a23f9d2daae69bcb2955e01b6ba710d0f4b3523","tid":517857,"uid":104213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T17:26:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eser